StEstMaker
==========

This maker contains the new C++ version of the 
External Silicon Tracker which tries to associate
SVT/SSD hits to the reconstructed TPC tracks.
This maker replaces the old FORTRAN version previously
stored under pams/global/est.

Main authors : Piotr Leszczyñski, Adam Maliszewski (Warsaw University of Technology)
Main contributors : Lilian Martin, Christelle Roy (SUBATECH Nantes)

Documentation
=============

The Maker documentation (a la StarClassLibrary) is located in the
doc subdirectory in Latex format. ps or pdf version can be created
with the associated Makefile


